Aye Aye Coin on-chain info

Welcome to the on-chain info page.
Through this web page you can get the unwrapped and wrapped Aye Aye coin balances and unwrapped transactions of a specified ETH address.

This page requires a web3 browser to work (for example chrome+metamask). No wallet connect needed, just an ethereum connection
